Compute the coefficients:
- $a_0 = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_{-\pi}^\pi f(x) \, dx = \frac{2\pi^2}{3}$. 
- $a_n = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_{-\pi}^\pi \cos(n x) f(x) \, dx = (-1)^n \frac{4}{n^2}$.
- $b_n = \frac{1}{\pi} \int_{-\pi}^\pi \sin(n x) f(x) \, dx = 0$.

